      "body" : "On AskUbuntu, there also were some deprecated answers, so I answered <a href=\"https://askubuntu.com/a/1161572/830570\">how to install Java 7 or 8 on a more recent Ubuntu</a>. This answer also solves the &quot;PPA DISCONTINUED&quot; Problem. You can also consider <a href=\"http://www.ubuntuupdates.org/package/webupd8_java/precise/main/base/oracle-java7-set-default\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">this link</a> to set <code>JAVA_HOME</code> and <code>PATH</code> as <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/20565550/4575793\">Brent Robinson mentioned in his answer</a>."
